org.apache.flex.compiler.asdoc

Interface IMetadataParserASDocDelegate


  • public interface IMetadataParserASDocDelegate
    Interface used by the MetadataParser to recored information about ASDoc comments encountered while parsing meta-data.

    Implementations of this interface that record ASDoc data are stateful and can not be shared between MetadataParser instances.
